item.description:
Contact Bill - 603.557.6055 or bill@imaginetworks.com

Regular Wimp Volleyball too slow for you? Want to ramp up the intensity and get in on a fast team game?
Come out and give Wallyball a try! It's volleyball inside a racquetball court. You can play the rebounds and it's a lot of fun. Best part is that you never have to chase the ball very far! ;)

Every Wed night at 8pm til 10pm @ the NAC (Nashua Athletic Club)

Wallyball is free for NAC members, non-menbers can be sponsored in for a small fee ($9) + you will need to sign an injury waiver.
item.name: Wednesday Night Wallyball!
